text.paragraph:
Carefully consider the potential benefits and risks of naproxen, naproxen sodium and other treatment options before deciding to use naproxen and naproxen sodium tablets. Use the lowest effective dose for the shortest duration consistent with individual patient treatment goals (see 
                        WARNINGS
                     ).

Naproxen and naproxen sodium are contraindicated for the treatment of peri-operative pain in the setting of coronary artery bypass graft (CABG) surgery (see 
                        WARNINGS
                     ).
